\c 16
\s Rudo rwaDhavhidhi kuna Jehovha
\d Rwiyo Mikitami rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Ndichengetei, Mwari, nokuti ndinovimba nemi.
\v 2 Ndakati kuna Jehovha, "Ndimi Ishe wangu; Kunze kwenyu handine chinhu chakanaka."
\v 3 Kana vari vatsvene, vari panyika, Ndivo vakaisvonaka vandinofarira zvikuru.
\v 4 Kuchema kuchawanzwa kwavanovigira mumwe mwari zvipo; Zvipiriso zvavo zvinodururwa zveropa handingazvidururi, Namazita avo handingaarevi nemiromo yangu.
\v 5 Jehovha ndiye mugove wenhaka yangu nowomukombe wangu; Munochengeta mugove wangu.
\v 6 Rwonzi rwokuyera rwakandiyerera nzvimbo dzakanaka; Zvirokwazvo, nhaka yangu yakaisvonaka.
\v 7 Ndicharumbidza Jehovha akandipa mano, Zvirokwazvo, itsvo dzangu dzinondidzidzisa
\s panguva dzousiku.
\p
\v 8 Ndakaisa Jehovha pamberi pangu nguva dzose;
\s Zvaari kurudyi rwangu, handingazununguswi.
\p
\v 9 Naizvozvo mwoyo wangu unofara, kukudzwa kwangu kunofarisisa; Nyama yanguo ichagara
\s yakachengetwa.
\p
\v 10 Nokuti hamungasiyi mweya wangu muSheori;
\s Hamungatenderi mutsvene wenyu kuti aone kuora.
\p
\v 11 M_ue,\vancliratidza nzira youpenyu; Mufaro wakazara uri pamberi pangu;
\s Paruoko rwenyu rworudyi panezvinofadza nokusingaperi.
